-1158388906.text: "Moreover, Rk3 induced the activation of caspase-8, -9, and -3, promoted changes in mitochondrial membrane potential, decreased the expression of Bcl-2, increased the expression of Bax, and caused the release of cytochrome c, which indicated that the apoptosis inducing effects of Rk3 were triggered via death receptor mediated mitochondria dependent pathways."
